message.body: Morning! Didn't get home in time to get to the farm last night so I went this morning. Ground was pretty hard and lucky said he didn't care for it. So pretty much I stretched his Legs for 15 min :)
Hey, thanks for getting him out!
Brenna has someone who might come see him Saturday. She asked about jumping him 3'6 and if he has changes (lolol). I'll keep you posted!
Ha oh my! Brenna had told me that someone was coming :)
Oh good! We'll see how it goes!
Wanna ride lucky on Sunday too? I have a shelter dog thing in the city, not sure when I'll get back
That Monday I'm going to NYC with my mom. Sorry
